  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 7 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 21 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 9 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 22</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You must be under the effects of Inuzuka Ryuu: Soutourou and be able to charge the target. This technique is a charge attack made against a single target, but is treated as a Line area (width equal to your FS) that knocks all creatures it encounters aside (to the outside edge of the Line) if they fail a Fortitude save.<br><br>The target of the charge is not knocked back, and the charge attack deals double damage if using a claw or bite attack, though it suffers a 20% miss chance.<br><br>You must make a Fortitude save (DC 15) to avoid becoming @Condition[nauseated;duration=1]{nauseated} for 1 round.</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> Each step reduces the miss chance by 5%.</p>\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
